# GitHub Reply Style

When writing GitHub comments (PR reviews, issue replies, etc.):

- **Keep it short** — get to the point, no filler
- **Add warmth** — thank contributors, acknowledge effort, use phrases like `Nice work!`, `Great catch!`, `Thanks @xxx!`
- **Be direct** — say what needs to change clearly, pair with encouragement
